comments: Barnes (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Okoro (CLE).
Sexton (CLE) makes contact to Fox's (SAC) arm as he enters his shooting motion during his jump shot.

Replay review of the foul called on Fox (SAC) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Fox (SAC) makes contact to Garland's (CLE) body during his drive to the basket and there is no clear and conclusive video evidence to overturn the call on the floor.
Holmes (SAC) legally contests Okoro's (CLE) jump shot attempt.
Hield (SAC) commits a take foul on Stevens (CLE).
Haliburton (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Okoro (CLE).
Sexton (CLE) makes contact to Fox's (SAC) arm and body during his finish at the rim.
Fox (SAC) reaches in and avoids making contact to Sexton's (CLE) arm as he contests his driving shot attempt.

After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of a goaltending on Holmes (SAC) is confirmed. 
 Holmes makes contact with the ball after hits the backboard during Sexton's (CLE) driving shot attempt.  The game clock is reset to 00:01.6.
